code: @Override protected EitherSerializer<L, R> createOuterSerializerWithNestedSerializers(TypeSerializer<?>[] nestedSerializers) {     @SuppressWarnings("unchecked")     TypeSerializer<L> leftSerializer = (TypeSerializer<L>) nestedSerializers[0].     @SuppressWarnings("unchecked")     TypeSerializer<R> rightSerializer = (TypeSerializer<R>) nestedSerializers[1].     return new EitherSerializer<>(leftSerializer, rightSerializer). }

@Override protected TypeSerializer<?>[] getNestedSerializers(EitherSerializer<L, R> outerSerializer) {     return new TypeSerializer<?>[] { outerSerializer.getLeftSerializer(), outerSerializer.getRightSerializer() }. }
